small in size but big in creative talent
id creations is an independent graphic design studio based near leeds, west yorkshire. launched in 2010 the company was created by creative consultant and graphic designer, nichola jackson. during this time nichola has worked with local and international clients to deliver creative and imaginative design solutions. nichola has accomplished a de montfort university degree in graphic design and has over 10 years experience in the professional creative industry. specialising in identity, branding, literature and web design, id creations can provide a friendly yet professional approach to suit any project large or small. id creations strive to build strong relationships with our clients and gain a clear understanding of their business objectives. working directly with the designer rather than an account handler ensures that the clients' ideas are reflected in the final design and influences the success of a project. previous position:metalfx technology â€“ design and marketing specialist
